        rus-sym {
            bindings = <
&none   &none        &kp LS(N7)       &kp EXCL    &kp LS(N2)  &kp LPAR  &kp EQUAL  &none         &none          &none       &trans        &kp RPAR
&trans  &kp KP_PLUS  &kp KP_MULTIPLY  &none       &none       &none     &none      &kp KP_MINUS  &none          &none       &trans        &none
&trans  &trans       &trans           &kp LS(N6)  &kp PRCNT   &none     &kp UNDER  &none         &kp LS(SLASH)  &kp KP_DOT  &kp KP_SLASH  &none
                                      &kp BSLH    &trans      &trans    &trans     &trans        &trans
            >;
